Question: You are given the chance to learn how to play a new instrument. Which one would you choose and why?
Answer:
i would like to choose panio. first of all, i can sit there, which will let me rest during playing. this is important because in this case i will find more time doing it. second, it uses both hands, so it will benefit my brain in a good way. third, i have a friend teaching the panio, so it will be easy for me to find a good teacher.